Sentencas: A novel design of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) which utilizes a thick film (<20 mu m) as an electrolyte support is developed and tested.
Titulo: Thick-film electrolyte (thickness <20 μm)-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The sintered 16 mu m-thickyttria-stabilizecl zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film is mounted on a 1-mm thick YSZ ring by sintering the two pieces together.
Titulo: Thick-film electrolyte (thickness <20 μm)-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: With this new configuration, it is possible to fabricate a thick (<20 mu m) electrolyte-supported SOFC and measure the power density of the unit cell.
Titulo: Thick-film electrolyte (thickness <20 μm)-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: With LSCF (La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta) as a cathode and Ni-YSZ as a composite anode, the cell with a 16 mu m-thick YSZ electrolyte achieves a high performance, i.e., a maximum power density of 590 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Thick-film electrolyte (thickness <20 μm)-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This value is comparable with that of most anode-supported SOFCs using YSZ electrolytes.
Titulo: Thick-film electrolyte (thickness <20 μm)-supported solid oxide fuel cells
